title: Arena Breakout - Official Closed Beta Announcement Trailer

media:group.media:title: Arena Breakout - Official Closed Beta Announcement Trailer
media:group.media:description:
Check out the latest trailer for Arena Breakout, an upcoming tactical free-to-play first-person shooter game. Arena Breakout has a planned global release on iOS and Android mobile devices in early 2023. The first closed beta test for Android users in Australia, New Zealand, and the Philippines will be available later this month.
